title: [Landrat's Magic Shoppe]
[Landrat's Weaponry]
description: Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A gold-leafed mistwood cabinet and a flexible willow woven basket sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on an unfinished wooden floor.

Beneath a varnished golden oak ceiling, a ruby-eyed grinning skull hangs on one of the ribbed black willow walls.  A gold-leafed mistwood cabinet and a flexible willow woven basket sit in opposite corners while a carved ebonwood dinghy rests on a polished oak floor.
